txtRns.text: The following are forms noted within the handbook. Forms are separated by action. Some forms are Agency
only specific and require only Agency action (as noted in the “Agency Use Only” column). Some forms are
optional and should be used at the discretion of the lender (as noted in the “Optional Use by Lender” column).
All forms are in-fillable format and can be accessed from the Rural Development Instructions website at:
